name: Cubic Emotion Pack
description:
Cubic Emotion Pack

This pack consists of 48 cubic emotion faces in solid, gradient, and outline formats. Including these faces into your design process or user interfaces take your design to the next level and connect with people's emotions. According to your preference, you can choose either solid color variant, gradient variant, or outline variant. 

Duplicate and remix the community file, then share on social media and tag your fellow designers.
